        "Speaker": {
          "type": "cexostring",
          "value": ""
        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Yes. Which is precisely why this report is disturbing. Something that size should not have survived transport, confinement, or decades of neglect. Yet the station logs suggest it adapted. The interior is now a sealed hunting ground. Power flickers. Life support is unstable. Several lower decks have been reduced to wreckage. Whatever is in there has made the station its nest."
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "__struct_id": 4,
        "ActionParams": {
          "type": "list",
          "value": []
        },
        "Animation": {
          "type": "dword",
