          "value": ""
        },
        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Good. Enter the station, put the creature down, and recover proof of the kill. Return here afterward. And one more thing-if you find any surviving logs intact, leave them. I care more about the dragon being dead than I do about how it learned to thrive in there."
          }
        }
